Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:07.25,Chiha-poem,Default,0000,0000,0000,,None are left who know me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:10.47,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:12.83,Chiha-main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
